high_descs: Head right to the black vanity with sinks.
Open the lower right cabinet under the left sink, pick up the red towel from inside and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the white toilet on the right.
Put the red towel on the left side of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Place a towel on a toilet tank.

high_descs: turn right and walk over to the bathroom sink
grab a wash cloth out from the bottom left cabinet
turn around and walk back over to the toilet on the right side corner of the room
place the wash cloth above the toilet
anns.task_desc: place a wash cloth above the toilet

high_descs: take a few steps forward and turn to the right and go to the sink
open the bottom right sink cabinet door and take out the red rag from the cabinet
turn to the left twice and go to the wall and turn to the right and go to the toilet
put the rag on the toilet tank
anns.task_desc: Place a red rag on the toilet tank
